                "collapsible_LUPFGt": {
                  "type": "collapsible",
                  "name": "Collapsible",
                  "settings": {
                    "label": "<strong>What’s actually in this stack?</strong>",
                    "metafield_namespace_key": "product.smart.faqs",
                    "metafield_image_key": "image",
                    "metafield_label_key": "question",
                    "accordion_class": "accordion",
                    "content": "<p>The Metabolic Balance Stack includes two products: Berberine (1 bottle, 30 capsules, 30-day supply) and Magnesium Glycinate (1 bottle, 60 capsules, 30-day supply). Berberine uses FenuMat® technology for 6.2× better absorption and contains 1000mg Berberine HCl per capsule. Magnesium uses Chelamax® chelation and Capsoil® liposomal delivery for up to 8× better absorption, sourced from Dead Sea mineral-rich waters.</p>",
                    "show": false,
                    "metafield_content_key": "answer",
                    "metafield_default_state": "open_first",
                    "auto_close_siblings": true,
                    "dynamic_content_type": "default",
                    "custom_css": "& {\n}",
                    "hide_if_empty": "none"
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                },
                "collapsible_zkFnQa": {
                  "type": "collapsible",
                  "name": "Collapsible",
                  "settings": {
                    "label": "<strong>Do I take both products at the same time?</strong>",
                    "metafield_namespace_key": "product.smart.faqs",
                    "metafield_image_key": "image",
                    "metafield_label_key": "question",
                    "accordion_class": "accordion",
                    "content": "<p>This varies with each of our products. We always suggest you consult your doctor and make sure you are not exceeding the recommended daily values of nutrients.</p>",
                    "show": false,
                    "metafield_content_key": "answer",
                    "metafield_default_state": "open_first",
                    "auto_close_siblings": true,
                    "dynamic_content_type": "default",
                    "custom_css": "& {\n}",
                    "hide_if_empty": "none"
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                },
                "collapsible_GwxcwM": {
                  "type": "collapsible",
                  "name": "Collapsible",
                  "settings": {
                    "label": "<strong>How long until I feel results?</strong>",
                    "metafield_namespace_key": "product.smart.faqs",
                    "metafield_image_key": "image",
                    "metafield_label_key": "question",
                    "accordion_class": "accordion",
                    "content": "<p><em>When taking a supplement of any kind during pregnancy or breastfeeding, we recommend consulting a physician and showing them our nutritional labels to make the best decision for you.</em></p>",
                    "show": false,
                    "metafield_content_key": "answer",
                    "metafield_default_state": "open_first",
                    "auto_close_siblings": true,
                    "dynamic_content_type": "default",
                    "custom_css": "& {\n}",
                    "hide_if_empty": "none"
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                },
                "collapsible_H66LeE": {
                  "type": "collapsible",
                  "name": "Collapsible",
                  "settings": {
                    "label": "<strong>Is it safe to take long-term?</strong>",
                    "metafield_namespace_key": "product.smart.faqs",
                    "metafield_image_key": "image",
                    "metafield_label_key": "question",
                    "accordion_class": "accordion",
                    "content": "<p>Yes, all of our products are produced in GMP and NSF certified facilities and undergo third-party testing to verify quality and consistency. While dietary supplements are not evaluated by the FDA for disease diagnosis or treatment, we stand behind their safety and transparency, with rigorous testing on every batch.</p>",
                    "show": false,
                    "metafield_content_key": "answer",
                    "metafield_default_state": "open_first",
                    "auto_close_siblings": true,
                    "dynamic_content_type": "default",
